title: Elemental Princess: Royal Lines
description: ELEMENTAL PRINCESS by M.M. Roethig *Prequel to RaineKaesen, an elemental princess, lives on a distant star called Maia. She loves Alwen, but as her sworn protector they're forbidden to be together. Promised to a cruel man, Kaesen will do whatever is necessary to change the stars and be allowed to love her Alwen.
author: M.M. Roethig
